CryptoAve,com,is,a,secure,exchange,service,for,purchasing,and,selling,Bitcoin,and,other,cryptocurrencies,CryptoAve,com,hosts,a,public,API,that,developers,can,implement,into,rd,party,applications,to,display,information,on,market,statistics,and,real,time,currency,prices,The,API,accepts,HTTP,requests,per,hour,period,and,returns,JSON,formatted,responses